jcatapult-deployer

Packages
org.jcatapult.deployer This package contains the application managers and the deployer interface used by deployer.groovy scripts to deploy resources to domain environments
org.jcatapult.deployer.domain This package contains all domain objects used by the org.jcatapult.deployer.service services
org.jcatapult.deployer.guice Contains the Guice module to bind interfaces to concrete implementation for dependency injection
org.jcatapult.deployer.net This package contains APIs necessary to perform SCP and SSH Execs processes
org.jcatapult.deployer.service This package contains the service APIs for the jcatapult deployer framework
org.jcatapult.deployer.utils
